Package application

Class Employee

java.lang.Object
application.Employee
Direct Known Subclasses:
Fulltime, Parttime
public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
The employee class is the superclass of every class that describes a different kind of employee. When an object of type employee is made and the specifications are set, whatever commands are called will invoke the inherited attributes of that method at which matches the actions that the command expects.
Author:
Ceceliachollette-Dickson, Nidaansari
